#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the Open File &kde; standard dialog, to open a <literal role="
"\"extension\">.sgf</literal> file (&kigo; game file), which contains a saved "
"game."
msgstr ""
